OL,3,CFirms offer no festive cheer to Reeves
OL,4,Cwith gloomy outlook for 2025
OL,6,FBusinesses have issued a stark warning
OL,7,Fto Rachel Reeves that the economy is
OL,8,F"headed for the worst of all worlds"
OL,9,Fwith activity expected to fall sharply
OL,10,Fin the first three months of 2025.
OL,12,FA major survey by the Confederation of
OL,13,FBritish Industry (CBI) found firms
OL,14,Fexpected to reduce both output and
OL,15,Fhiring.
OL,17,FThe Chancellor's hike to employers'
OL,18,Fnational insurance, set to rake in
OL,19,Faround #25 billion a year, was
OL,20,Fhighlighted as one of the reasons for
OL,21,Fthe gloomy outlook.
