OL,6,FAlpesh Paleja, the CBI's interim
OL,7,Fdeputy chief economist, said: "There
OL,8,Fis little festive cheer in our latest
OL,9,Fsurveys, which suggest that the
OL,10,Feconomy is headed for the worst of all
OL,11,Fworlds ` firms expect to reduce both
OL,12,Foutput and hiring, and price growth
OL,13,Fexpectations are getting firmer.
OL,15,F"Businesses continue to cite the
OL,16,Fimpact of measures announced in the
OL,17,FBudget ` particularly the rise in
OL,18,Femployer NICs ` exacerbating an
OL,19,Falready tepid demand environment.
