OL,6,F"As we head into 2025, firms are
OL,7,Flooking to the Government to boost
OL,8,Fconfidence and to give them a reason
OL,9,Fto invest, whether that's long overdue
OL,10,Fmoves to reform the apprenticeship
OL,11,Flevy, supporting the health of the
OL,12,Fworkforce through increased
OL,13,Foccupational health incentives or a
OL,14,Freform of business rates.
