OL,6,F"In the longer term, businesses will
OL,7,Fbe looking to the industrial strategy
OL,8,Fto provide the stability and certainty
OL,9,Fwhich can unlock innovation and
OL,10,Finvestment ` and provide that much-
OL,11,Fneeded growth for the economy which
OL,12,Fcan deliver prosperity for firms and
OL,13,Fhouseholds alike."
OL,15,FThe CBI's growth indicator survey,
OL,16,Fbased on responses from 899 companies
OL,17,Fbetween November 25 and December 12,
OL,18,Ffound expectations for growth are now
OL,19,Fat their weakest since November 2022
OL,20,Fin the aftermath of Liz Truss's
OL,21,Fchaotic tenure in No 10.
