OL,6,FThe predicted fall in activity is
OL,7,Fbroad-based: business volumes in the
OL,8,Fservices sector are anticipated to
OL,9,Fdecline while distribution sales and
OL,10,Fmanufacturing output are also expected
OL,11,Fto fall sharply in the three months to
OL,12,FMarch.
OL,14,FThe survey found a 24 percentage point
OL,15,Fgap between companies which gave
OL,16,Fnegative responses on expected output
OL,17,Fand those which gave positive
OL,18,Fresponses, a worse position than in
OL,19,FNovember when there was a 10-point gap.
