OL,13,Funexpectedly contracted in October
OL,14,Fthis year, marking two months in a row
OL,15,Fof negative growth for the first time
OL,16,Fsince the pandemic.
OL,18,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,19,F(ONS) said gross domestic product
OL,20,F(GDP) contracted 0.1% in October.
